Product description

Crafted from high-quality TPR (Thermoplastic Rubber) and PU (Polyurethane), these shoes showcase a harmonious blend of durability and comfort. The TPR outsole provides a reliable grip and ensures stability on various surfaces, making them suitable for both urban exploration and leisurely strolls.
Benefits:-
Comfortable Fit: Designed with a flat and round silhouette, these shoes provide a comfortable fit that allows your feet to rest naturally. The well-crafted shape minimizes discomfort even during extended wear.
Durability: Crafted with a combination of TPR (Thermoplastic Rubber) and PU (Polyurethane), these shoes are built to last. The TPR outsole enhances durability and provides a reliable grip on various surfaces, making them suitable for different environments.
Stability: The TPR outsole not only adds durability but also offers stability. Whether you're walking on city streets or exploring outdoor paths, these shoes provide a secure footing for your every step.
Easy Pairing: Thanks to their versatile design, these lace-up sneakers are easy to pair with a wide range of outfits.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
